         MACRO                                                          TXTHDR
         TXTHDR                                                         TXTHDR
*********************************************************************** TXTHDR
*                                                                     * TXTHDR
*  DSECT to map a txt card header                                     * TXTHDR
*                                                                     * TXTHDR
*********************************************************************** TXTHDR
TXTHDR   DSECT                                                          TXTHDR
TXTHADR  DS    XL3             24 bit address of first byte of text     TXTHDR
TXTHLEN  DS    X               Number of bytes of text data             TXTHDR
TXTHDRLN EQU   *-TXTHDR       Length of text card.                      TXTHDR
         MEND                                                           TXTHDR
